er'&gt;8&lt;/span&gt;--&lt;span-class='chapter-title'&gt;Diccionarios&lt;/span&gt;"&gt;&lt;span class="chapter-number"&gt;8&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class="chapter-title"&gt;Diccionarios&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="hidden quarto-markdown-envelope-contents" data-render-id="quarto-int-sidebar:quarto-sidebar-section-4"&gt;Unidad 4: Python Avanzado&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="hidden quarto-markdown-envelope-contents" data-render-id="quarto-int-sidebar:/unidades/unidad4/5_programacion_oo.html&lt;span-class='chapter-number'&gt;9&lt;/span&gt;--&lt;span-class='chapter-title'&gt;Programación-Orientada-a-Objetos&lt;/span&gt;"&gt;&lt;span class="chapter-number"&gt;9&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class="chapter-title"&gt;Programación Orientada a Objetos&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="hidden quarto-markdown-envelope-contents" data-render-id="quarto-int-sidebar:/unidades/unidad4/6_modulos.html&lt;span-class='chapter-number'&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;--&lt;span-class='chapter-title'&gt;Módulos&lt;/span&gt;"&gt;&lt;span class="chapter-number"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class="chapter-title"&gt;Módulos&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="hidden quarto-markdown-envelope-contents" data-render-id="quarto-int-sidebar:/unidades/unidad4/7_pypi.html&lt;span-class='chapter-number'&gt;11&lt;/span&gt;--&lt;span-class='chapter-title'&gt;Uso-de-Pypi&lt;/span&gt;"&gt;&lt;span class="chapter-number"&gt;11&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class="chapter-title"&gt;Uso de Pypi&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="hidden quarto-markdown-envelope-contents" data-render-id="quarto-int-sidebar:/unidades/unidad4/8_publicar_pypi.html&lt;span-class='chapter-number'&gt;12&lt;/span&gt;--&lt;span-class='chapter-title'&gt;Públicar-un-paquete-en-Pypi&lt;/span&gt;"&gt;&lt;span class="chapter-number"&gt;12&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class="chapter-title"&gt;Públicar un paquete en Pypi&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="hidden quarto-markdown-envelope-contents" data-render-id="quarto-int-sidebar:/uni